{"word":"H155 - אַדֶּרֶת - ʼaddereth - ad-deh'-reth - Garment","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אַדֶּרֶת</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>ʼaddereth"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>ad-deh'-reth"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Garment"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"அங்கி, சால்வை, மகிமை, இரட்டு, போர்வை - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"glory, cloak,"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. மகிமை (glory, splendor, magnificence)"},{"paragraph":"2. சால்வை (mantle, cloak made of fur or fine material) - தீர்க்கதரிசியின் வஸ்திரம் a (prophet's garment)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Feminine of <a href=\"#/H117 - אַדִּיר - ʼaddîyr - ad-deer'/117\">H117</a>; something <i>ample</i> (as a <i>large</i> vine, a <i>wide</i> dress); also the same as <a href=\"#/H145 - אֶדֶר - ʼeder - eh'-der/145\">H145</a>: - garment, glory, goodly, mantle, robe."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H115 - אֲדֹורַיִם - ʼĂdôwrayim - ad-o-rah'-yim/115\">H115</a>, <a href=\"#/H117 - אַדִּיר - ʼaddîyr - ad-deer'/117\">H117</a>, <a href=\"#/H142 - אָדַר - ʼâdar - aw-dar'/142\">H142</a>, <a href=\"#/H143 - אֲדָר - ʼĂdâr - ad-awr'/143\">H143</a>, <a href=\"#/H145 - אֶדֶר - ʼeder - eh'-der/145\">H145</a>, <a href=\"#/H146 - אַדָּר - ʼAddâr - ad-dawr'/146\">H146</a>, <a href=\"#/H152 - אֲדְרַמֶּלֶךְ - ʼĂdrammelek - ad-ram-meh'-lek/152\">H152</a>, <a href=\"#/H155 - אַדֶּרֶת - ʼaddereth - ad-deh'-reth/155\">H155</a>"}]}